Package: ep
Type: Package
Title: Calculate earned premium by policy
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2014-01-13
Author: Yours Truly
Maintainer: Yours Truly <yours.truly@somewhere.net>
Description: Given a policy level data.frame with columns named
  writtenpremium, effectivedate, and expirationdate, and given an ascending sequence 
  of 'asof' dates, this package's sole function, 'earnPremium', will earn each
  policy's writtenpremium between the asof dates.
License: GPL
Depends: plyr
